creator: Vision IT
descriptionHtml:
- do you wanna know where and in which conditions your train, and fleet? Do you care about your passengers’ safety and comfort?

- Train Tracker(TT) brings all assets under 1 umbrella: Operation and Maintenance

- Train Tracker(TT) is digitalising Trains and making them smart

- Shows the train on a map including its real time Digital Twin, location, faults and CCTV on the same screen

- Maintenance Management: Preventive, Corrective and Conditioned Based Maintenance including Personnel Management with performance reviews

- It is a remote system to monitor, watch, surveillance and inform many kinds of data and information on a real time basis from the rolling stocks.

Important Note:
TT is private app for Operation and Maintenance Companies for their fleet, depot and personnel. Therefore, IT IS NOT INTENDED FOR PUBLIC USE.

- Train Tracker(TT) is digitalising Trains and making them smart

- Shows the train on a map including its real time Digital Twin, location, faults and CCTV on the same screen

- Maintenance Management: Preventive, Corrective and Conditioned Based Maintenance including Personnel Management with performance reviews

- It is a remote system to monitor, watch, surveillance and inform many kinds of data and information on a real time basis from the rolling stocks.

Important Note:
TT is private app for Operation and Maintenance Companies for their fleet, depot and personnel. Therefore, IT IS NOT INTENDED FOR PUBLIC USE.
